{"serial": "12016", "department_serial": 11, "code": "EL3071", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Cross-Linguistic Comparisons A", "ch": "跨語言對比分析A"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Li, Ming-Yi"], "ch": ["李明懿"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "A", "room": "110"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "英美語文學系", "en": "Department of English"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 24, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1. 能掌握語言對比分析的基本理論和概念\n2. 能從詞彙、語法、語義和語用等面向進行跨語言觀察和分析\n3. 能增強對語言結構和功能的理解，培養對語言特徵的敏感度\n4. 能應用語料庫資源以及研究方法(資料收集和數據分析等)進行對比分析\n5. 能理解不同語言使用規約差異並將所學應用於實際語言學習和教學中，提高跨語言溝通能力和教學技巧。", "en": "Students who attend the course and complete all the learning tasks will:\n1. be able to unerstand the basic theories and concepts of comtrastive analysis.\n2. be able to conduct cross-language observation and analysis from the aspects of vocabulary, grammar, semantics and pragmatics\n3. can enhance understanding of language structures and functions\n4. be able to apply corpus resources and research methods (data collection and data analysis, etc.) for CA\n5. be able to understand the differences in usage conventions of different languages."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 對比分析理論基礎\n2. 語料庫與對比分析\n3. 詞彙對比分析\n4. 語法對比分析\n5. 語義對比分析\n6. 篇章語用對比", "en": "1. Theoretical Basis of Contrstive Analysis (CA)\n2. Corpus and CA\n3. CA on words\n4. CA on sentence structures\n5. CA and semantics\n6. CA on discourse and pragmatics"}, "textbook": {"ch": "James, C. 1980. Contrastive Analysis. New York: Longman.\n潘文國 2010. 《漢英比分析概論》. 北京：商務印書館。\n劉月華、潘燁、故煒 1996.《實用現代漢語語法》. 台北：師大書苑。\n屈承熹、紀宗仁 2000.《漢語認知功能語法》. 台北：文鶴。\nLi, C. N. ＆ Thompson, S. A. 1981. Mandarin Chinese: \nA Functional Reference Grammar；黃宣範1992譯《漢語語法》。台北:文鶴。\n呂叔湘 2007.《現代漢語八百詞-增訂版》. 中國社會科學院。\n陳俊光 2012. 《對比分析與教學應用》. 文鶴。\n彭忍鋼 2009. 《對比分析與英漢翻譯》. 陝西人民出版社。\n陳俊光 2010. 《篇章分析與教學應用》. 新學林。\n鄧守信 2022. 《現代漢語語法講義》. 書林", "en": "James, C. 1980. Contrastive Analysis. New York: Longman.\n潘文國 2010. 《漢英比分析概論》. 北京：商務印書館。\n劉月華、潘燁、故煒 1996.《實用現代漢語語法》. 台北：師大書苑。\n屈承熹、紀宗仁 2000.《漢語認知功能語法》. 台北：文鶴。\nLi, C. N. ＆ Thompson, S. A. 1981. Mandarin Chinese: \nA Functional Reference Grammar；黃宣範1992譯《漢語語法》。台北:文鶴。\n呂叔湘 2007.《現代漢語八百詞-增訂版》. 中國社會科學院。\n陳俊光 2012. 《對比分析與教學應用》. 文鶴。\n彭忍鋼 2009. 《對比分析與英漢翻譯》. 陝西人民出版社。\n陳俊光 2010. 《篇章分析與教學應用》. 新學林。\n鄧守信 2022. 《現代漢語語法講義》. 書林"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30%", "en": "30%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "Class participation60％\nattending (10％)\nclass performance (20％)\nweekly assignment (30％)\nfinal project 40％", "en": "Class participation60％\nattending (10％)\nclass performance (20％)\nweekly assignment (30％)\nfinal project 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週一13:00-15:00，週二10:00-11:00，週四14:00-16:00", "en": "13:00-15:00 on Manday, 10:00-11:00 on Tuesday, 14:00-15:00 on Thursday"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "本學期此課程採用16+2週模式。學生課堂學習16週，學期中之後，教師將依學生學習情況和專題進行個別指導及諮詢，為時2週以上。", "en": "The students of this course will study in classroom for 16 weeks. After the middle of the semester, teachers will provide individual guidance and consultation based on students‘ learning conditions and topics."}, "domain": {"ch": "語言學與英語教學", "en": "語言學與英語教學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "英文閱讀解析與寫作論述", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "英語溝通與文化跨越", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞與多元創意", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "人文思維與社會關懷", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我